  "prompt": "Which laptop should I buy under 60000?",
  "response": "If you're looking to buy a laptop under \u20b960,000 in India, there are several great options available across various brands, catering to different needs such as productivity, gaming, or entertainment. Here are some recommendations as of 2023:\n\n---\n\n### **1. Lenovo Ideapad Slim 3 (AMD Ryzen 5)**\n- **Price**: ~\u20b955,000\n- **Specs**:  \n  - AMD Ryzen 5 5500U  \n  - 8GB RAM, 512GB SSD  \n  - 15.6\" FHD IPS Display  \n- **Best For**: Productivity, multitasking, and casual use.\n\n---\n\n### **2. HP Pavilion 14 (Intel i5)**\n- **Price**: ~\u20b958,000\n- **Specs**:  \n  - Intel Core i5-1240P  \n  - 8GB RAM, 512GB SSD  \n  - 14\" FHD IPS Display  \n- **Best For**: Office work, students, and everyday use.\n\n---\n\n### **3. Acer Aspire 5 (AMD Ryzen 5)**\n- **Price**: ~\u20b956,000\n- **Specs**:  \n  - AMD Ryzen 5 5500U  \n  - 8GB RAM, 512GB SSD  \n  - 15.6\" FHD IPS Display  \n- **Best For**: General productivity and multimedia.\n\n---\n\n### **4. Asus Vivobook 15 (Intel i5)**\n- **Price**: ~\u20b959,000\n- **Specs**:  \n  - Intel Core i5-12500H  \n  - 8GB RAM, 512GB SSD  \n  - 15.6\" FHD IPS Display  \n- **Best For**: Content creation and light gaming.\n\n---\n\n### **5. Dell Inspiron 3525 (AMD Ryzen 5)**\n- **Price**: ~\u20b954,000\n- **Specs**:  \n  - AMD Ryzen 5 5625U  \n  - 8GB RAM, 512GB SSD  \n  - 15.6\" FHD Anti-Glare Display  \n- **Best For**: Everyday tasks and business use.\n\n---\n\n### **6. MSI Modern 14 (Intel i5)**\n- **Price**: ~\u20b959,000\n- **Specs**:  \n  - Intel Core i5-1155G7  \n  - 8GB RAM, 512GB SSD  \n  - 14\" FHD IPS Display  \n- **Best For**: Portability and lightweight design.\n\n---\n\n### **7. Realme Book Slim (Intel i5)**\n- **Price**: ~\u20b956,000\n- **Specs**:  \n  - Intel Core i5-1135G7  \n  - 8GB RAM, 512GB SSD  \n  - 14\" 2K Display  \n- **Best For**: Students and professionals looking for a sleek design.\n\n---\n\n### **8. Xiaomi Notebook Ultra (Intel i5)**\n- **Price**: ~\u20b959,000\n- **Specs**:  \n  - Intel Core i5-11320H  \n  - 8GB RAM, 512GB SSD  \n  - 15.6\" 3.2K Display  \n- **Best For**: High-resolution display and premium build.\n\n---\n\n### **Key Features to Look For:**\n- **Processor**: AMD Ryzen 5 or Intel Core i5 (11th Gen or newer).  \n- **RAM**: 8GB (expandable to 16GB is a plus).  \n- **Storage**: 512GB SSD for faster performance.  \n- **Display**: 14\" or 15.6\" FHD IPS for better clarity.  \n- **Battery Life**: 5+ hours for portability.  \n\n---\n\n### **Tips for Buying:**\n- Check for discounts during festive sales (Amazon Great Indian Festival, Flipkart Big Billion Days).  \n- Look for extended warranty or accidental damage protection.  \n- Compare prices across platforms like Amazon, Flipkart, and official brand websites.  \n\nLet me know if you need help narrowing down the options!",
